w21xxkdgq6.name: NTU South Spine Male Musolla
w21xxkdgq6.address: 50 Nanyang Avenue, S3 Level 2, South Spine, Singapore 639798
w21xxkdgq6.directions:
Take lift from Nanyang Business School (NBS), Block S3.
NBS Building is beside The Hive.

From Hive, building is connected to NBS at Level B2.
Take the first lift after crossing the bridge from Hive to NBS, and go to Level 2 (Roof).
